PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?year ?country ?countryLabel ( COUNT( ?awardStmt ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?person wdt:P31 wd:Q5 ; wdt:P27 ?country ; p:P166 ?awardStmt .
  ?awardStmt ps:P166 ?awardItem ; pq:P585 ?time .
  ?awardItem wdt:P279 * wd:Q7191 .
  BIND( YEAR( ?time ) AS ?year ) OPTIONAL {
    ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?countryLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
GROUP BY ?year ?country ?countryLabel
ORDER BY ?year ?countryLabel
